message:
Yesterday Karena and Mia walked in the Hillbilly Hike Half Marathon, 10k & Greubel 5k covered in Band-Aids, to shine a spotlight on Human Trafficking. They had a goal of 100 supporters for the Band-Aids to ERASE Child Trafficking Fundraiser. They still have a little ways to go. Will you be 1 of the 100? You can still show support. Pictures by Chasing Light Photography

https://www.facebook.com/donate/392156498123808/?fundraiser_source=external_url

#Bethedifference #EndHumanTrafficking #HillbillyHike #Iowa #CreatingChange
